<section id="products" class="scroll-mt-20 bg-slate-50 py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-indigo-700">Two ways to collaborate</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 break-keep text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-slate-950 sm:text-5xl">만드는 과정과, 일하는 방식</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">목표는 다르지만 약속은 같습니다. AI를 설명하는 데 그치지 않고 실제로 무엇을 만들고 어떻게 일했는지 보여줍니다.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <article class="group flex min-h-[29rem] flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-blue-200 bg-white p-7 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl sm:p-9">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-blue-50 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-black tracking-[0.16em] text-blue-700">BUILD WITH AI</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-400">01 / CHATDOX</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-14">
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-700">무엇을 만들 수 있는가?</p>
          <h3 class="mt-3 break-keep text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-slate-950">AI와 함께 SaaS 구축하기</h3>
          <p class="mt-5 max-w-lg text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">기획부터 배포까지 실제 서비스 하나를 완성하는 실전 과정입니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-12">
          <%= link_to chatdox_path, class: "inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white transition group-hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-blue-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2" do %>
            Chatdox 자세히 보기 <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="group flex min-h-[29rem] flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-violet-200 bg-white p-7 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl sm:p-9">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-violet-50 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-black tracking-[0.16em] text-violet-700">WORK WITH AI</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-400">02 / CLAUDOX</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-14">
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-violet-700">어떻게 함께 일할 것인가?</p>
          <h3 class="mt-3 break-keep text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-slate-950">클로드가 들어온 날,<br>팀이 달라졌다</h3>
          <p class="mt-5 max-w-lg text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">AI가 질문, 기록과 업무 프로세스를 바꾸는 실제 협업 이야기입니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-12">
          <%= link_to claudox_path, class: "inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-violet-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white transition group-hover:bg-violet-700 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-violet-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2" do %>
            Claudox 자세히 보기 <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
